### Changes
- [x] Use typescript to parse tsconfig, more standard.
- [ ] `import { json5 } from '../utilsBundle';` is removed, if nobody is using `utilBundle.json5`, it should be removed, lazy to have a glance.
- [ ] `interface Tsconfig` field `extends?: string;` should be removed, because after PR, it always return an extended tsconfig parsed by typescript, so field `extends` is never included in return, lazy to have a glance if other code need that field.

